com.laegler.fastbpmn.fastBpmn

Interface FTask

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, FAbstractElement, FActivity, FBaseElement, FFlowElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FTaskImpl

    public interface FTask
extends FActivity
    A representation of the model object 'FTask'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Task Type
    • Event
    • Message
    • Data IO
    • Data Object

    See Also:
    FastBpmnPackage.getFTask()
